# Documentation

## Overview

This folder contains all project documentation related to the SAP S/4HANA-inspired ERP implementation for hospitality operations.

The purpose of this documentation is to provide a clear record of project objectives, design decisions, methodologies, implementation details, findings, and future recommendations.

